text: Rochester is an unincorporated community in Andrew County, in the U.S. state of Missouri. ==History== Rochester was platted in 1848. The name is a transfer from Rochester, England. A post office called Rochester was established in 1844, and remained in operation until 1935. ==References== Category:Unincorporated communities in Andrew County, Missouri Category:Unincorporated communities in Missouri
title: Rochester, Missouri
